CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 14, 1956, p. A12, reads: "Shoe Repair - Glenn R. Zellars (left), watches as Sequoyah L. Payne and Richard L. Kipp practice on a pair of shoes. These boys attend South Vocational High School and are enrolled in shoe repair class. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Glenn R. Zellars watching Sequoyah L. Payne operating machinery, with Richard L. Kipp on right, in shoe repair class in South Vocational High School
